<DOC><DOCNO> WSJ871007-0176 </DOCNO><HL> Financing Business:Petroleum Helicopters Inc.</HL><DD> 10/07/87</DD><SO> WALL STREET JOURNAL (J)</SO><IN> PHELSTOCK MARKET, OFFERINGS (STK) </IN><TEXT>   PETROLEUM HELICOPTERS INC. said it plans to offer 2.6 million to three million shares of its nonvoting common stock before year end. The provider of helicopter services for companies engaged in offshore oil and natural gas exploration said proceeds will be used to reduce long-term debt. The New Orleans company wouldn't identify the underwriters. </TEXT></DOC>